Definition: a book of the Old Testament that tells the story of Ruth who was not an Israelite but who married an Israelite and who stayed with her mother-in-law Naomi after her husband died
Synonyms: Book_of_Ruth, book, i, Hagiographa, p, Old_Testament, a, of, the, Old, Testament, that, tells, story, who, was, not, an, Israelite, but, married, and, stayed, with, her, mother-in-law, Naomi, after, husband, died
Category: noun.communication
